Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Melton is one of Melbourne's fastest growing suburbs, with 11 new suburbs slated for the area, it is quickly emerging as a high density residential precinct in need of Quick Service Retail operators to cater for the growing population.    

This site which sees prime exposure to Melton Highway, is anchored by 7-Eleven and allows convenient access to public transport, Melbourne and Melton Airports, and major arterial roads. With Rapid Tune, Qahwa Bean Coffee now secured there is a drive-thru tenancy remaining. Don't miss this significant opportunity to be in a prime position within this high profile location. 
 
*approx.

Located 35km to the north-west of Melbourne, West Pines Lifestyle Centre is poised to become the dominant Large Format Retail site in the Melton Catchment. The Centre is located on Melton Highway, a major arterial which connects to High St in the West and merges into the Western Highway to the South. The site sees over 53,000* vehicles pass daily.

The centre, which is being delivered by Citinova, has been expertly designed in order to achieve maximised site exposure and functionality. The development includes; a Large Format Retail Precinct which comprises of a 17,842sqm Bunnings Warehouse, a Homemaker Centre including 11 tenancies and 13,350sqm of retail space, four fast food PAD sites with committed tenants including Carl’s Junior, a Caltex Service Station, three story Office Tower, Conference Centre, Motorcycle Retailers Kawasaki & Honda, Auto Workshops with committed tenants Bridgestone & Battery World, Car dealerships, a Childcare and 959 car spaces. 

- High profile location, within close proximity Melton Town Centre

- Projected population growth expected to reach 233,000* people by 2033 - increasing by 3.8% annually

- Adjacent A Grade retailers; Chemist Warehouse, The Good Guys, Pet Stock, Repco

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: JOIN WEST PINES MELTON - MULTIPLE OPPORTUNITIES AVAILABLE
